OL,7,FJuries in sexual assault cases could
OL,8,Fhear from expert witnesses to tackle
OL,9,Fthe persistent problem of rape myths at
OL,10,Ftrials, according to proposals being
OL,11,Fconsidered by the independent body that
OL,12,Freviews laws for England and Wales.
OL,14,FThe Law Commission is due to publish a
OL,15,Flist of recommendations for improving
OL,16,Fthe trial process for sexual offences
OL,17,Fin February 2023, with hopes it will
OL,18,Flead to the better treatment of
OL,19,Fcomplainants while ensuring defenders
OL,20,Fget a fair trial.
OL,3,CJuries in rape cases could hear from
OL,4,Cexperts to dispel myth that 'real
OL,5,Cvictims should be upset'
